column5: I dropped out in school, because I feel exhausted and anxious about everything, like just some fucking words from my classmates that is related to me. I just wanted to die, because I do not have any future in this fucking world.
We're same, it's like "Hey God! Please kill me right now while I am taking a bath.", "Please let me die if I sit on this chair." I want to die, but I don't like to kill my own self.
